===Function===
This template shows the POTD from Commons

A generated list of images for use in this template can be copy-pasted from [http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Freestyle_nl/POTD_nl here]. For the [[Template:POTD commons/Captions]] (used for the captions) use [http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Freestyle_nl/POTD_caption this] generated list.

===Parameters===
* thumb=yes - show as thumbnail
* title=yes - show the title (only in combination with thumb=yes)
* caption=no - don't show the captions
* float=left/right - for floating the thumbnail left or right (default=left) 

===Example===

<code><nowiki>{{Template:POTD commons|thumb=yes|title=yes|float=right}}</nowiki></code> - this will show a thumbnailed version, floated right, with the title and captions.


